{"tid":1710733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［善用優勢］揭竿起義 一呼百應 如何善用中大人的力量","createTime":"2019-11-12T08:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:10:45.000Z","uid":199517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6425d98d42418df98334cbe2d444237d0fc7577d","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"香港人同狗相比之下有咩優勢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係人多同靈活啊！</span></span><br />\n係武裝完全不對等，敵暗我明嘅情況下<br />\n敵人可以清楚我哋嘅部署，以一擋百<br />\n再多嘅人入中大 成效不大 反而會增加傷亡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相反，要班狗以人力資源較少嘅情況下對抗多處強力示威就會變跑狗</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">葵荃人，油尖旺人，將軍澳觀塘人 起身做嘢啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"f683b592355c98d253c9529b4127221260a72873","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d52faa1a3c4891799ad0cff6da91374628928d86","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好咁做"},{"pid":"778dd7a437cf0a09b7964dd0991cdafbb7f758aa","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"人民公僕做嘢好辛苦架，又要入新屋嶺屌女又要着重裝全港跑"},{"pid":"06ee1a17c3375ed03814a30dd1a78232c75adea9","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c36354246b98cbcd57952e8a3f78b2bca8797171","tid":1710733,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229d43bfc95cda22b46b2380ad5ebf581a8b87cf","tid":1710733,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c645e1fc0f2c268b87c680e9797f90e9ff25be67","tid":1710733,"uid":199517,"like":0,"disli